author: ETA PRIME
description:
In this video, we test out the all-new Intel Arc Pro B50 low-profile workstation GPU paired with AMD’s Ryzen 9800X3D, the best gaming CPU on the market right now.
Everyone knows the Arc Pro B50 was designed for professional workloads—but can it actually handle AAA gaming? We put it to the test in some of the biggest titles out there, including:
* Doom: The Dark Ages
* Borderlands 4
* Cyberpunk 2077
* And more!
Surprisingly, this tiny low-profile GPU delivers way more performance than expected. If you’re curious about budget builds, compact PCs, or just want to see what the Arc Pro B50 can really do, you won’t want to miss this one.
